# tRPC Best Practices for Knitly Monorepo

## Overview
- **Centralized API Layer**: Use tRPC for type-safe API communication between client and server
- **Database Separation**: All database queries MUST be in `@workspace/database`, never in tRPC routers
- **Authentication**: Use Supabase Auth context in tRPC procedures
- **Server/Client Pattern**: Follow established server-side prefetching and client-side usage patterns

## Architecture Patterns

### 🏗️ File Structure
```
apps/main/trpc/
├── init.ts              # tRPC initialization, context, procedures
├── server.tsx           # Server-side tRPC utilities, prefetch helpers  
├── client.tsx           # Client-side provider and hooks
├── query-client.ts      # React Query configuration
└── routers/
    ├── _app.ts          # Main router composition
    ├── transactions.ts  # Feature-specific routers
    ├── analytics.ts
    ├── emails.ts
    └── feedback.ts
```

### 🔧 Server Configuration

#### ✅ tRPC Initialization ([init.ts](mdc:apps/main/trpc/init.ts))
```typescript
// init.ts - Core tRPC setup
import { createClient } from '@/supabase/server';
import { initTRPC } from '@trpc/server';
import { TRPCError } from '@trpc/server';
import { cache } from 'react';

export interface Context {
  userId: string | null;
}

export const createTRPCContext = cache(async () => {
  try {
    const supabase = await createClient();
    const { data: { user }, error } = await supabase.auth.getUser();
    
    return { 
      userId: user?.id ?? null 
    } satisfies Context;
  } catch (error) {
    console.error('tRPC context creation error:', error);
    return { userId: null } satisfies Context;
  }
});

const t = initTRPC.context<Context>().create({
  // transformer: superjson, // Add if using complex types
});

export const createTRPCRouter = t.router;
export const createCallerFactory = t.createCallerFactory;
export const baseProcedure = t.procedure;

export const protectedProcedure = baseProcedure.use(async ({ ctx, next }) => {
  if (!ctx.userId) {
    throw new TRPCError({ code: "UNAUTHORIZED" });
  }
  return next({ ctx });
});
```

#### ✅ API Route Handler ([route.ts](mdc:apps/main/app/api/trpc/[trpc]/route.ts))
```typescript
// app/api/trpc/[trpc]/route.ts
import { fetchRequestHandler } from '@trpc/server/adapters/fetch';
import { createTRPCContext } from '@/trpc/init';
import { appRouter } from '@/trpc/routers/_app';

const handler = (req: Request) =>
  fetchRequestHandler({
    endpoint: '/api/trpc',
    req,
    router: appRouter,
    createContext: createTRPCContext,
